Before you start processing crypto transactions

1. use payed plan for Firebase for external api connection
2. sign up block.io, generate pinKey, get apiKey for currency
3. firebase functions:config:set keys.wallet_pin="YOUR_PIN_KEY" keys.wallet_api="YOUR_API_KEY"
4. use payed plan for block.io for web hooks activation (or test api key)
5. activate notifications for balance changes for all your addresses via https://block.io/docs/notifications/nodejs
6. test balance via https://console.firebase.google.com/project/YOUR_PROJECT_KEY/functions/list

